caption.p: PCAs with important loading variables for Dutch and British brands that are produced by the same manufacturer. Panel ( A), triglycerides; ( B), phospholipids. DG, diglycerides; PC, phosphatidylcholine; PE, phosphatidylethanolamine; PI, phosphatidylinositol; TG, triglyceride. 1, 0–6 mo; 2, 6–12 mo; 3, 12–24 mo; 24 mo+; H, 0–6 mo (hungry); NL, Dutch formula.
